{"tid":1074513,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★ 索假紙不果 支那婦大鬧瑪麗醫院急症室","createTime":"2019-03-23T12:26:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-24T05:32:07.000Z","uid":19454,"like":145,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":72,"replies":[{"pid":"4995d3c88bd56610ef7756896327b03fe9d9bd64","tid":1074513,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T12:26:00.000Z","msg":"公立醫院資源緊絀，前線醫護人員人手短缺，壓力已經爆煲；學法官話齋：「忙到一頭煙，仲要遇到刁民攪攪震！」令醫護人員更添麻煩。<br />\n<br />\n日前一名網民喺 Facebook PO 文稱在瑪麗醫院目擊一名<span style=\"color: red;\">操不純正廣東話嘅大媽坐喺輪椅上要求醫生開病假紙</span>，醫生就答只可以提供到診紙，大媽開始不滿反問：「我聽日點返工？」<br />\n<br />\n醫生即刻話：「點返工係你嘅問題，直家冇事你可以走。」<br />\n<br />\n開始失控：「呢間醫院係你㗎？你叫我走我就走，冇假紙點走？」<br />\n<br />\n醫生無理佢，反問：「到院紙要唔要？唔要我撕咗佢！」<br />\n<br />\n大媽就賴死唔走，仲大叫：「我係講道理!!」<br />\n<br />\n醫生見到咁嘅情況就即時叫護士請保安過嚟 &hellip; 之後一名保安就將大媽送出急症室 !!<br />\n<br />\n完！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://circle01.life/view1/8619/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcircle01.life%2Fview1%2F8619%2F&d=INFrb%2BpCZNVkt1J9J2ljEG7D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=82fad5a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://circle01.life/view1/8619/</a>"},{"pid":"035f01ed4f51bafa0576257722d34c12e0f1575b","tid":1074513,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":52,"score":-51,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T12:26:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qwN3sK7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqwN3sK7.png&h=3eaf24ff&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1576d1e24743c27b4b078315ca369d32ed8af3dd","tid":1074513,"uid":35014,"like":124,"dislike":1,"score":123,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T12:27:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4e6c5b2a243240bcce98aaafceafdd2a0ef6656e","tid":1074513,"uid":37661,"like":119,"dislike":1,"score":118,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T12:29:24.000Z","msg":"乜做雞都要假紙？"},{"pid":"262590acc2cfff494d90fccbe961ca4a34bbb8ee","tid":1074513,"uid":19454,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"quote":{"pid":"1576d1e24743c27b4b078315ca369d32ed8af3dd","tid":1074513,"uid":35014,"like":124,"dislike":